[SN]TITLE[SN]
Is this the world's muddiest tractor race?

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
These farmers in central Thailand have been taking a rather muddy break from work - with an annual tractor race!

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
23 April 2017 Last updated at 15:08 BST
The farmers are usually busy working in paddy fields, where they use their tractors to plough and carry rice.
But once a year, they make special alterations to their tractors so that they'll be as powerful as possible racing around the course.
